610478,124,609,13,20,1,111,7,Tattha atthapabhedassa sallakkhaṇavibhāvanavavatthānakaraṇasamatthaṃ atthe pabhedagataṃ ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā. 
610479,124,609,21,27,1,107,6,Dhammapabhedassa sallakkhaṇavibhāvanavavatthānakaraṇasamatthaṃ dhamme pabhedagataṃ ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā. 
610480,124,609,28,34,1,117,6,Niruttipabhedassa sallakkhaṇavibhāvanavavatthānakaraṇasamatthaṃ niruttābhilāpe pabhedagataṃ ñāṇaṃ niruttipaṭisambhidā. 
610481,124,609,35,43,1,116,6,Paṭibhānapabhedassa sallakkhaṇavibhāvanavavatthānakaraṇasamatthaṃ paṭibhāne pabhedagataṃ ñāṇaṃ paṭibhānapaṭisambhidā. 
610482,124,609,44,45,1,11,1,Vuttañhetaṃ–
610483,124,610,2,28,1,152,15,"‘ ‘ Atthe ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā, dhamme ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā, tatra dhammaniruttābhilāpe ñāṇaṃ niruttipaṭisambhidā, ñāṇesu ñāṇaṃ paṭibhānapaṭisambhidā’’ ti( vibha.718). "
610484,124,611,2,12,1,83,10,Ettha ca hetuanusārena araṇīyato adhigantabbato ca saṅkhepato hetuphalaṃ attho nāma. 
610485,124,611,13,29,1,98,12,"Pabhedato pana yaṃkiñci paccayuppannaṃ, nibbānaṃ, bhāsitattho, vipāko, kiriyāti ime pañca dhammā attho. "
610486,124,611,30,38,1,78,8,Taṃ atthaṃ paccavekkhantassa tasmiṃ atthe pabhedagataṃ ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā. 
610487,124,611,39,43,1,27,3,Dhammoti saṅkhepato paccayo. 
610488,124,611,44,59,1,83,14,"So hi yasmā taṃ taṃ atthaṃ vidahati pavatteti ceva pāpeti ca, tasmā dhammoti vuccati. "
610489,124,611,60,87,1,188,22,"Pabhedato pana yo koci phalanibbattako hetu, ariyamaggo, bhāsitaṃ, kusalaṃ, akusalanti ime pañca dhammā dhammo, taṃ dhammaṃ paccavekkhantassa tasmiṃ dhamme pabhedagataṃ ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā. "
610490,124,611,88,90,1,14,2,Vuttampi cetaṃ–
610491,124,612,2,28,1,169,15,"‘ ‘ Dukkhe ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā, dukkhasamudaye ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā, dukkhanirodhe ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā’’ ti( vibha.719). "
610492,124,613,2,11,1,74,8,"Atha vā hetumhi ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā, hetuphale ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā. "
610493,124,613,12,25,1,99,12,"Ye dhammā jātā bhūtā sañjātā nibbattā abhinibbattā pātubhūtā, imesu dhammesu ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā. "
610494,124,613,26,41,1,112,14,"Yamhā dhammā te dhammā jātā bhūtā sañjātā nibbattā abhinibbattā pātubhūtā, tesu dhammesu ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā. "
610495,124,613,42,49,1,78,6,"Jarāmaraṇe ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā, jarāmaraṇasamudaye ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā. "
610496,124,613,50,58,1,103,7,"Jarāmaraṇanirodhe ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā, jarāmaraṇanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā. "
610497,124,613,59,84,1,149,15,"Jātiyā, bhave, upādāne, taṇhāya, vedanāya, phasse, saḷāyatane, nāmarūpe, viññāṇe, saṅkhāresu ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā, saṅkhārasamudaye ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā. "
610498,124,613,85,94,1,99,7,"Saṅkhāranirodhe ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā , saṅkhāranirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā."
610499,124,614,2,17,1,53,9,"‘ ‘ Idha bhikkhu dhammaṃ jānāti– suttaṃ, geyyaṃ… pe… vedallaṃ. "
610500,124,614,18,21,1,31,3,Ayaṃ vuccati dhammapaṭisambhidā. 
610501,124,614,22,28,1,41,6,So tassa tasseva bhāsitassa atthaṃ jānāti–
610502,124,614,29,50,1,91,12,"‘ ayaṃ imassa bhāsitassa attho, ayaṃ imassa bhāsitassa attho’ ti, ayaṃ vuccati atthapaṭisambhidā( vibha.724)."
610503,124,615,2,7,1,20,4,‘ ‘ Katame dhammā kusalā? 
610504,124,615,8,38,1,192,25,"Yasmiṃ samaye kāmāvacaraṃ kusalaṃ cittaṃ uppannaṃ hoti somanassasahagataṃ ñāṇasampayuttaṃ rūpārammaṇaṃ vā… pe… dhammārammaṇaṃ vā yaṃ yaṃ vā panārabbha, tasmiṃ samaye phasso hoti… pe… avikkhepo hoti. "
610505,124,615,39,42,1,17,3,Ime dhammā kusalā. 
610506,124,615,43,61,1,92,10,"Imesu dhammesu ñāṇaṃ dhammapaṭisambhidā, tesaṃ vipāke ñāṇaṃ atthapaṭisambhidā’’ tiādi vitthāro( vibha.725). "
610507,124,616,2,31,1,219,22,"Tasmiṃ atthe ca dhamme ca sabhāvanirutti abyabhicāravohāro abhilāpo, tasmiṃ sabhāvaniruttābhilāpe māgadhikāya sabbasattānaṃ mūlabhāsāya‘‘ ayaṃ sabhāvanirutti, ayaṃ na sabhāvaniruttī’’ ti pabhedagataṃ ñāṇaṃ niruttipaṭisambhidā. "
610508,124,616,32,47,1,165,15,Yathāvuttesu tesu ñāṇesu gocarakiccādivasena vitthārato pavattaṃ sabbampi ñāṇamārammaṇaṃ katvā paccavekkhantassa tasmiṃ ñāṇe pabhedagataṃ ñāṇaṃ paṭibhānapaṭisambhidā. 
610509,124,616,48,65,1,184,17,Iti imāni cattāri paṭisambhidāñāṇāni sayameva bhagavatā adhigatāni atthadhammādike tasmiṃ tasmiṃ attano visaye avisaṃvādanavasena aviparītākārappavattiyā tathāni avitathāni anaññathāni. 
