610562,124,635,2,87,1,551,44,"Tathā ‘‘ sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā– satisambojjhaṅgo, dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo, vīriyasambojjhaṅgo, pītisambojjhaṅgo, passaddhisambojjhaṅgo, samādhisambojjhaṅgo, upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo’’ ti( paṭi. ma.2.17; saṃ. ni.5.185) evaṃ sarūpato yāyaṃ lokuttaramaggakkhaṇe uppajjamānā līnuddhaccapatiṭṭhānāyūhanakāmasukhattakilamathānuyogaucchedasassatābhinivesādīnaṃ anekesaṃ upaddavānaṃ paṭipakkhabhūtā satiādibhedā dhammasāmaggī, yāya ariyasāvako bujjhati, kilesaniddāya uṭṭhahati, cattāri vā saccāni paṭivijjhati, nibbānameva vā sacchikaroti, sā dhammasāmaggī‘‘ bodhī’’ ti vuccati, tassā bodhiyā aṅgāti bojjhaṅgā. "
610563,124,635,88,101,1,77,9,Ariyasāvako vā yathāvuttāya dhammasāmaggiyā bujjhatīti katvā‘‘ bodhī’’ ti vuccati. 
610564,124,635,102,132,1,342,22,"Tassa bodhissa aṅgāti bojjhaṅgāti evaṃ sāmaññalakkhaṇato , upaṭṭhānalakkhaṇo satisambojjhaṅgo, pavicayalakkhaṇo dhammavicayasambojjhaṅgo, paggahalakkhaṇo vīriyasambojjhaṅgo, pharaṇalakkhaṇo pītisambojjhaṅgo, upasamalakkhaṇo passaddhisambojjhaṅgo, avikkhepalakkhaṇo samādhisambojjhaṅgo paṭisaṅkhānalakkhaṇo upekkhāsambojjhaṅgoti evaṃ visesalakkhaṇato."
610565,124,636,2,7,1,30,4,‘ ‘ Tattha katamo satisambojjhaṅgo? 
610566,124,636,8,34,1,190,18,"Idha bhikkhu satimā hoti paramena satinepakkena samannāgato, cirakatampi cirabhāsitampi saritā hoti anussaritā’’ tiādinā( vibha.467) sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ aññamaññūpakāravasena ekakkhaṇe pavattidassanato."
610567,124,636,35,40,1,30,3,‘‘ Tattha katamo satisambojjhaṅgo? 
610568,124,636,41,60,1,105,11,"Atthi ajjhattaṃ dhammesu sati, atthi bahiddhā dhammesu satī’’ tiādinā( vibha.469) tesaṃ visayavibhāvanāpavattidassanato."
610569,124,636,61,66,1,30,3,‘‘ Tattha katamo satisambojjhaṅgo? 
610570,124,636,67,90,1,142,11,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu satisambojjhaṅgaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ, virāganissitaṃ, nirodhanissitaṃ, vosaggapariṇāmin’’ tiādinā( vibha.471) bhāvanāvidhidassanato."
610571,124,636,91,97,1,29,4,‘‘ Tattha katame satta bojjhaṅgā? 
610572,124,636,98,119,1,131,16,"Idha bhikkhu yasmiṃ samaye lokuttaraṃ jhānaṃ bhāveti… pe… tasmiṃ samaye satta bojjhaṅgā honti, satisambojjhaṅgo… pe… upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo. "
