610631,124,655,2,6,1,32,4,Kathaṃ tathehi agatoti tathāgato? 
610632,124,655,7,13,1,82,6,Bodhisambhārasambharaṇe tappaṭipakkhappavattisaṅkhātaṃ natthi etassa gatanti agato. 
610633,124,655,14,25,1,142,11,So panassa agatabhāvo maccheradānapāramiādīsu aviparītaṃ ādīnavānisaṃsapaccavekkhaṇādinayappavattehi ñāṇehīti tathehi ñāṇehi agatoti tathāgato. 
610634,124,656,2,14,1,126,12,Atha vā kilesābhisaṅkhārappavattisaṅkhātaṃ khandhappavattisaṅkhātameva vā pañcasupi gatīsu gataṃ gamanaṃ etassa natthīti agato. 
