611181,124,824,2,4,1,25,2,9 . Sikkhānisaṃsasuttavaṇṇanā 
611182,124,825,2,20,1,109,10,"46. Navame {sikkhānisaṃsā}ti ettha sikkhitabbāti sikkhā, sā tividhā adhisīlasikkhā, adhicittasikkhā, adhipaññāsikkhāti. "
611183,124,825,21,30,1,75,8,"Tividhāpi cesā sikkhā ānisaṃsā etesaṃ, na lābhasakkārasilokāti sikkhānisaṃsā. "
611184,124,825,31,48,1,147,15,"{Viharathā}ti sikkhānisaṃsā hutvā viharatha, tīsu sikkhāsu ānisaṃsadassāvino hutvā tāhi sikkhāhi laddhabbaṃ ānisaṃsameva sampassantā viharathāti attho. "
611185,124,825,49,63,1,106,12,"{Paññuttarā}ti tāsu sikkhāsu yā adhipaññāsikkhāsaṅkhātā paññā, sā uttarā padhānā visiṭṭhā etesanti paññuttarā. "
611186,124,825,64,72,1,54,7,"Ye hi sikkhānisaṃsā viharanti, te paññuttarā bhavantīti. "
611187,124,825,73,88,1,124,12,"{Vimuttisārā}ti arahattaphalasaṅkhātā vimutti sāraṃ etesanti vimuttisārā, yathāvuttaṃ vimuttiṃyeva sārato gahetvā ṭhitāti attho. "
611188,124,825,89,107,1,121,16,"Ye hi sikkhānisaṃsā paññuttarā ca, na te bhavavisesaṃ patthenti, apica kho vibhavaṃ ākaṅkhantā vimuttiṃyeva sārato paccenti. "
611189,124,825,108,126,1,216,16,"{Satādhipateyyā}ti jeṭṭhakakaraṇaṭṭhena sati adhipateyyaṃ etesanti satādhipateyyā adhipati eva adhipateyyanti katvā, catūsu satipaṭṭhānesu suppatiṭṭhitacittā kāyānupassanādimukhena samathavipassanābhāvanānuyuttāti attho. "
611190,124,826,2,33,1,264,26,"Atha vā {sikkhānisaṃsā}ti bhikkhave, evarūpe dullabhakkhaṇapaṭilābhe tividhasikkhāsikkhanameva ānisaṃsaṃ katvā viharatha, evaṃ viharantā ca paññuttarā paññāya uttarā lokuttarapaññāya samannāgatā hutvā viharatha, evaṃbhūtā ca vimuttisārā nibbānasārā anaññasārā viharatha. "
611191,124,826,34,54,1,167,17,"Tathābhāvassa cāyaṃ upāyo, yaṃ satādhipateyyā viharatha, satipaṭṭhānabhāvanāya yuttappayuttā hotha, sabbattha vā satārakkhena cetasā viharathāti evamettha attho veditabbo. "
611192,124,826,55,87,1,246,26,"Iti bhagavā tīsu sikkhāsu bhikkhū niyojento yathā tā sikkhitabbā, yena ca pāripūriṃ gacchanti, taṃ saṅkhepeneva dassetvā idāni yathānusiṭṭhaṃ paṭipajjamānānaṃ phalavisesadassanena tassā paṭipattiyā amoghabhāvaṃ pakāsento‘‘ sikkhānisaṃsānan’’ tiādimāha. "
611193,124,826,88,90,1,17,2,Taṃ vuttatthameva. 
611194,124,827,2,10,1,80,7,"Gāthāsu paripuṇṇasikkhan ti aggaphalappattiyā parisuddhasikkhaṃ, asekkhanti attho. "
611195,124,827,11,18,1,61,7,Apahānadhamman ti ettha pahānadhammā vuccanti kuppā vimuttiyo. 
611196,124,827,19,23,1,40,4,Pahānadhammoti hi hānadhammo kuppadhammo. 
