611201,124,828,2,12,1,76,7,"{Tasmā}ti yasmā sikkhāpāripūriyā ayaṃ jarāpāraṅgamanapariyosāno ānisaṃso, tasmā. "
611202,124,828,13,16,1,17,2,{Sadā}ti sabbakālaṃ. 
611203,124,828,17,30,1,90,9,"{Jhānaratā}ti lakkhaṇūpanijjhāne, ārammaṇūpanijjhāneti duvidhepi jhāne ratā, tato eva samāhitā. "
611204,124,828,31,43,1,110,11,Māraṃ sasenaṃ {abhibhuyyā}ti kilesasenāya anaṭṭhasenāya ca sasenaṃ anavasiṭṭhaṃ catubbidhampi māraṃ abhibhavitvā. 
611205,124,828,44,56,1,78,8,Devaputtamārassapi hi guṇamāraṇe sahāyabhāvūpagamanato kilesā‘‘ senā’’ ti vuccanti. 
