611221,124,842,2,4,1,20,2,10 . Jāgariyasuttavaṇṇanā 
611222,124,843,2,18,1,111,10,"47. Dasame {jāgaro}ti jāgarako vigataniddo jāgariyaṃ anuyutto, rattindivaṃ kammaṭṭhānamanasikāre yuttappayuttoti attho. "
611223,124,843,19,20,1,11,1,Vuttañhetaṃ–
611224,124,844,2,12,1,76,7,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pubbarattāpararattaṃ jāgariyānuyogamanuyutto hoti? "
611225,124,844,13,60,1,386,43,"Idha bhikkhu divasaṃ caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi cittaṃ parisodheti, rattiyā paṭhamaṃ yāmaṃ caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi cittaṃ parisodheti, rattiyā majjhimaṃ yāmaṃ dakkhiṇena passena sīhaseyyaṃ kappeti pāde pādaṃ accādhāya sato sampajāno uṭṭhānasaññaṃ manasi karitvā, rattiyā pacchimaṃ yāmaṃ paccuṭṭhāya caṅkamena nisajjāya āvaraṇīyehi dhammehi cittaṃ parisodheti. "
611226,124,844,61,74,1,65,6,Evaṃ bhikkhu pubbarattāpararattaṃ jāgariyānuyogamanuyutto hotī’’ ti( vibha.519). 
611227,124,845,2,9,1,61,6,"Casaddo sampiṇḍanattho, tena vakkhamāne satādibhāve sampiṇḍeti. "
611228,124,845,10,16,1,28,4,"{Assā}ti siyā, bhaveyyāti attho."
611229,124,845,17,28,1,42,7,‘‘ Jāgaro ca bhikkhu vihareyyā’’ ti ca paṭhanti. 
611230,124,845,29,43,1,144,12,Sabbattha sabbadā ca kammaṭṭhānāvijahanavasena satiavippavāsena sato {sampajāno}ti sattaṭṭhāniyassa catubbidhassapi sampajaññassa vasena sampajāno. 
611231,124,845,44,51,1,67,6,{Samāhito}ti upacārasamādhinā appanāsamādhinā ca samāhito ekaggacitto. 
611232,124,845,52,63,1,131,10,{Pamudito}ti paṭipattiyā ānisaṃsadassanena uttaruttari visesādhigamena vīriyārambhassa ca amoghabhāvadassanena pamudito pāmojjabahulo. 
611233,124,845,64,77,1,112,12,{Vippasanno}ti tato eva paṭipattibhūtāsu tīsu sikkhāsu paṭipattidesake ca satthari saddhābahulatāya suṭṭhu pasanno. 
611234,124,845,78,83,1,41,5,Sabbattha assāti sambandho vihareyyāti vā. 
611235,124,846,2,18,1,125,14,"Tattha kālavipassī ca kusalesu {dhammesū}ti tasmiṃ kāle vipassako, tattha vā kammaṭṭhānānuyoge kālavipassī kālānurūpaṃ vipassako. "
611236,124,846,19,22,1,15,3,Kiṃ vuttaṃ hoti? 
611237,124,846,23,77,1,517,50,"Vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā kalāpasammasanādivasena sammasanto āvāsādike satta asappāye vajjetvā sappāye sevanto antarā vosānaṃ anāpajjitvā pahitatto cittassa samāhitākāraṃ sallakkhento sakkaccaṃ nirantaraṃ aniccānupassanādiṃ pavattento yasmiṃ kāle vipassanācittaṃ līnaṃ hoti, tasmiṃ dhammavicayavīriyapītisaṅkhātesu, yasmiṃ pana kāle cittaṃ uddhataṃ hoti, tasmiṃ passaddhisamādhiupekkhāsaṅkhātesu kusalesu anavajjesu bojjhaṅgadhammesūti evaṃ tattha tasmiṃ tasmiṃ kāle, tasmiṃ vā kammaṭṭhānānuyoge kālānurūpaṃ vipassako assāti. "
611238,124,846,78,83,1,44,4,Satisambojjhaṅgo pana sabbattheva icchitabbo . 
611239,124,846,84,116,1,60,7,"Vuttañhetaṃ‘‘ satiñca khvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sabbatthikaṃ vadāmī’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.234; mi. pa.2.1.13). "
611240,124,846,117,129,1,107,11,"Ettāvatā puggalādhiṭṭhānāya desanāya jāgariyaṃ dassetvā yehi dhammehi jāgariyānuyogo sampajjati, te pakāseti. "
611241,124,847,2,28,1,209,19,"Evaṃ bhagavā āraddhavipassakassa bhikkhuno saṅkhepeneva saddhiṃ upakārakadhammehi sammasanacāraṃ dassetvā idāni tathā paṭipajjantassa paṭipattiyā avañjhabhāvaṃ dassento‘‘ jāgarassa, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno’’ tiādimāha. "
611242,124,847,29,42,1,147,11,"Tattha jāgariyānuyoge satisampajaññasamādānāni sabbatthakāni sammodapasādāvahāni, tattha kālavipassanā nāma vipassanāya gabbhaggahaṇaṃ paripākagataṃ. "
611243,124,847,43,61,1,144,17,"Upakkilesavimutte hi vīthipaṭipanne vipassanāñāṇe tikkhe sūre vahante yogino uḷāraṃ pāmojjaṃ pasādo ca hoti, tehi ca visesādhigamassa santikeyeva. "
611244,124,847,62,63,1,11,1,Vuttañhetaṃ–
611245,124,848,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Yato yato sammasati, khandhānaṃ udayabbayaṃ; "
611246,124,849,2,8,1,41,5,"Labhatī pītipāmojjaṃ, amataṃ taṃ vijānataṃ."
611247,124,850,2,9,1,42,5,"‘ ‘ Pāmojjabahulo bhikkhu, pasanno buddhasāsane; "
611248,124,851,2,21,1,49,6,"Adhigacche padaṃ santaṃ, saṅkhārūpasamaṃ sukhan’’ ti.( dha. pa.374,381); "
611249,124,852,2,18,1,173,16,Gāthāsu jāgarantā suṇāthetan ti etaṃ mama vacanaṃ ekanteneva pamādaniddāya avijjāniddāya pabodhanatthaṃ jāgarantā satisampajaññādidhammasamāyogena jāgariyaṃ anuyuttā suṇātha. 
611250,124,852,19,45,1,227,23,"Ye suttā te {pabujjhathā}ti ye yathāvuttaniddāya suttā supanaṃ upagatā, te tumhe jāgariyānuyogavasena indriyabalabojjhaṅge saṅkaḍḍhitvā vipassanaṃ ussukkāpentā appamādapaṭipattiyā tato pabujjhatha atha vā {jāgarantā}ti jāgaranimittā."
611251,124,852,46,74,1,87,15,"‘‘ Suṇāthetan’’ ti ettha‘‘ etan’’ ti vuttaṃ, kiṃ taṃ vacananti āha‘‘ ye suttā te pabujjhathā’’ tiādi. "
