611253,124,852,88,95,1,53,6,Suttā jāgaritaṃ {seyyo}ti idaṃ pabodhassa kāraṇavacanaṃ. 
611254,124,852,96,109,1,132,12,"Yasmā yathāvuttasupato vuttappakāraṃ jāgaritaṃ jāgaraṇaṃ atthakāmassa kulaputtassa seyyo pāsaṃsataro hitasukhāvaho, tasmā pabujjhatha. "
611255,124,852,110,117,1,54,7,Natthi jāgarato bhayan ti idaṃ tattha ānisaṃsadassanaṃ. 
611256,124,852,118,139,1,200,19,"Yo hi saddhādīhi jāgaraṇadhammehi samannāgamena jāgaro jaggati, pamādaniddaṃ na upagacchati, tassa attānuvādabhayaṃ parānuvādabhayaṃ daṇḍabhayaṃ duggatibhayaṃ jātiādinimittaṃ sabbampi vaṭṭabhayaṃ natthi. "
611257,124,853,2,8,1,39,3,{Kālenā}ti āvāsasappāyādīnaṃ laddhakālena. 
611258,124,853,9,12,1,17,2,{So}ti nipātamattaṃ. 
611259,124,853,13,34,1,184,17,"Sammā dhammaṃ {parivīmaṃsamāno}ti vipassanāya ārammaṇabhūtaṃ tebhūmakadhammaṃ sammā ñāyena yathā nibbindanavirajjanādayo sambhavanti, evaṃ parito vīmaṃsanto, sabbākārena vipassantoti attho. "
611260,124,853,35,44,1,51,7,"{Ekodibhūto}ti eko seṭṭho hutvā udetīti ekodi, samādhi. "
611261,124,853,45,52,1,47,7,So ekodi bhūto jāto uppanno etassāti ekodibhūto. 
