611288,124,858,2,14,1,98,11,Gāthāsu {abhūtavādī}ti parassa dosaṃ adisvāva abhūtena tucchena musāvādaṃ katvā paraṃ abbhācikkhanto. 
611289,124,858,15,31,1,60,11,{Katvā}ti yo vā pana pāpakammaṃ katvā‘‘ nāhaṃ etaṃ karomī’’ ti āha. 
611290,124,858,32,49,1,110,16,Ubhopi te pecca samā {bhavantī}ti te ubhopi janā ito paralokaṃ gantvā nirayaṃ upagamanato gatiyā samānā bhavanti. 
611291,124,858,50,58,1,45,7,"Tattha gatiyeva nesaṃ paricchinnā, na pana āyu. "
611292,124,858,59,70,1,77,10,"Bahuñhi pāpaṃ katvā ciraṃ niraye paccati, parittaṃ katvā appamattakameva kālaṃ. "
