611446,124,894,32,58,1,63,8,Dukkha -saddo pana‘‘ jātipi dukkhā’’ tiādīsu( dī. ni.2.387; vibha.190) dukkhavatthusmiṃ āgato.
611447,124,894,59,84,1,88,10,"‘‘ Yasmā ca kho, mahāli, rūpaṃ dukkhaṃ dukkhānupatitaṃ dukkhāvakkantan’’ tiādīsu( saṃ. ni.3.60) dukkhārammaṇe."
611448,124,894,85,101,1,44,5,‘‘ Dukkho pāpassa uccayo’’ tiādīsu( dha. pa.117) dukkhapaccaye.
611449,124,894,102,129,1,98,11,"‘‘ Yāvañcidaṃ, bhikkhave, na sukarā akkhānena pāpuṇituṃ, yāva dukkhā nirayā’’ tiādīsu( ma. ni.3.250) dukkhapaccayaṭṭhāne."
