611457,124,895,39,75,1,238,27,"Yadā hi sukhaṃ uppajjati, sakalasarīraṃ bhentaṃ maddantaṃ pharamānaṃ satadhotasappiṃ khādāpentaṃ viya, satapākatelaṃ makkhentaṃ viya, ghaṭasahassena pariḷāhaṃ nibbāpayamānaṃ viya ca‘‘ aho sukhaṃ, aho sukhan’’ ti vācaṃ nicchārayamānameva uppajjati. "
