611468,124,897,13,41,1,71,11,"‘‘ dvepi mayā, ānanda, vedanā vuttā, pariyāyena sukhā vedanā, dukkhā vedanā’’ ti( ma. ni.2.89). "
611469,124,897,42,75,1,192,18,"Katthaci tissopi visuṃ visuṃ sukhadukkhaadukkhamasukhabhāvena‘‘ sukhā vedanā ṭhitisukhā vipariṇāmadukkhā, dukkhā vedanā ṭhitidukkhā vipariṇāmasukhā, adukkhamasukhā vedanā ñāṇasukhā aññāṇadukkhā’’ ti( ma. ni.1.465). "
611470,124,897,76,79,1,30,3,Katthaci sabbāpi dukkhabhāvena. 
611471,124,897,80,103,1,65,9,"Vuttañhetaṃ‘‘ yaṃ kiñci vedayitaṃ, sabbaṃ taṃ dukkhasminti vadāmī’’ ti( saṃ. ni.4.259). "
611472,124,898,2,50,1,207,34,"Tattha siyā– yadi tisso vedanā yathā idha vuttā, aññesu ca edisesu suttesu abhidhamme ca evaṃ avatvā kasmā evaṃ vuttaṃ‘‘ yaṃ kiñci vedayitaṃ, sabbaṃ taṃ dukkhasminti vadāmī’’ ti,‘‘ dvepi mayā, ānanda, vedanā vuttā’’ ti ca? "
611473,124,898,51,56,1,44,4,"Sandhāyabhāsitametaṃ, tasmā sā pariyāyadesanā. "
611474,124,898,57,59,1,21,2,Vuttañhetaṃ bhagavatā–
611475,124,899,2,34,1,113,14,"‘ ‘ Saṅkhārāniccataṃ, ānanda, mayā sandhāya bhāsitaṃ saṅkhāravipariṇāmataṃ,‘ yaṃ kiñci vedayitaṃ, sabbaṃ taṃ dukkhasmin’’’ ti( saṃ. ni.4.259)."
611476,124,900,2,27,1,47,9,"‘ ‘ Dvepi mayā, ānanda, vedanā vuttā pariyāyenā’’ ti ca( saṃ. ni.4.259). "
611477,124,901,2,23,1,197,20,"Ettha hi sukhā adukkhamasukhāti imāsaṃ dvinnaṃ vedanānaṃ nippariyāyena dukkhabhāvo natthi, veneyyajjhāsayena pana tattha nicchandadassanatthaṃ pariyāyena dukkhabhāvo vuttoti sā tādisī pariyāyadesanā. "
611478,124,901,24,33,1,101,9,Ayaṃ pana vedanattayadesanā sabhāvakathāti katvā nippariyāyadesanāti ayamettha ācariyānaṃ samānakathā. 
611479,124,902,2,12,1,78,6,Vitaṇḍavādī panāha‘‘ dukkhatādvayavacanato pariyāyadesanāva vedanattayadesanā’’ ti. 
611480,124,902,13,52,1,210,25,"So‘‘ mā hevan’’ tissa vacanīyo, yasmā bhagavatā sabbāsaṃ vedanānaṃ dukkhabhāvo adhippāyavasena vutto‘‘ saṅkhārāniccataṃ, ānanda, mayā sandhāya bhāsitaṃ saṅkhāravipariṇāmataṃ‘ yaṃ kiñci vedayitaṃ, sabbaṃ taṃ dukkhasmin’’’ ti. "
611481,124,902,53,77,1,128,17,"Yadi panettha vedanattayadesanā pariyāyadesanā siyā,‘‘ idaṃ mayā sandhāya bhāsitaṃ tisso vedanā’’ ti vattabbaṃ siyā, na panetaṃ vuttaṃ. "
611482,124,903,2,15,1,65,7,"Apicāyameva vattabbo‘‘ ko, panāvuso, vedanattayadesanāya adhippāyo’’ ti? "
611483,124,903,16,32,1,106,12,"Sace vadeyya‘‘ mudukā dukkhā vedanā sukhā, adhimattā dukkhā, majjhimā adukkhamasukhāti veneyyajjhāsayena vuttā. "
611484,124,903,33,41,1,36,6,Tāsu hi na sattānaṃ sukhādivaḍḍhī’’ ti. 
611485,124,903,42,60,1,84,12,"So vattabbo– ko panāvuso dukkhavedanāya sabhāvo, yena‘‘ sabbā vedanā dukkhā’’ ti vucceyyuṃ? "
