611566,124,917,12,30,1,72,9,‘‘ yaṃ tasmiṃ samaye kāyikaṃ sukhaṃ kāyasamphassajaṃ sātaṃ sukhaṃ vedayitaṃ( dha. sa.449). 
611567,124,917,31,52,1,80,11,Yaṃ tasmiṃ samaye cetasikaṃ sukhaṃ cetosamphassajaṃ sātaṃ sukhaṃ vedayitan’’ ti( dha. sa.471) ca. 
611568,124,918,2,7,1,46,3,"{Pavattikālo}ti pavattikkhaṇo, pavattanākalanañca. "
611569,124,918,8,13,1,67,5,Pavattikkhaṇena hi sukhadukkhavedanānaṃ sukhadukkhabhāvo vavatthito. 
611570,124,918,14,15,1,7,1,Yathāha–
611571,124,919,2,35,1,121,16,"‘ ‘ Sukhā kho, āvuso visākha, vedanā ṭhitisukhā vipariṇāmadukkhā, dukkhā kho, āvuso visākha, vedanā ṭhitidukkhā vipariṇāmasukhā’’ ti( ma. ni.1.465). "
