611577,124,922,2,22,1,165,16,"Indriyan ti etā hi sukhādayo tisso vedanā sukhindriyaṃ, dukkhindriyaṃ, somanassindriyaṃ, domanassindriyaṃ, upekkhindriyanti adhipateyyaṭṭhena indriyato pañcadhā vibhattā. "
611578,124,922,23,30,1,60,6,"Kāyikañhi sātaṃ sukhindriyanti vuttaṃ, asātaṃ dukkhindriyanti. "
611579,124,922,31,39,1,70,7,"Mānasaṃ pana sātaṃ somanassindriyanti vuttaṃ, asātaṃ domanassindriyanti. "
