611600,124,927,34,37,1,28,3,Tena samannāgatattaṃ dasseti. 
611601,124,927,38,73,1,224,25,"Vedanā ca {pajānātī}ti‘‘ imā vedanā, ettakā vedanā’’ ti sabhāvato vibhāgato‘‘ aniccā dukkhā vipariṇāmadhammā’’ ti aniccādilakkhaṇato ca pubbabhāge tīhi pariññāhi parijānanto vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā ariyamaggena pariññāpaṭivedhena pajānāti. "
611602,124,927,74,78,1,39,4,Vedanānañca sambhavan ti samudayasaccaṃ. 
