611607,124,928,2,4,1,27,2,Tatiyasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
611608,124,929,2,4,1,24,2,4 . Dutiyavedanāsuttavaṇṇanā 
611609,124,930,2,14,1,97,8,53. Catutthe dukkhato {daṭṭhabbā}ti sukhavedanā vipariṇāmadukkhavasena dukkhāti ñāṇacakkhunā passitabbā. 
611610,124,930,15,25,1,120,9,Sallato {daṭṭhabbā}ti dunnīharaṇaṭṭhena antotudanaṭṭhena pīḷanaṭṭhena dukkhadukkhabhāvena dukkhavedanā sallanti passitabbā. 
611611,124,930,26,38,1,119,11,{Aniccato}ti hutvā abhāvato udayabbayavantato tāvakālikato niccapaṭipakkhato ca adukkhamasukhā vedanā aniccāti passitabbā. 
611612,124,930,39,71,1,217,24,"Kāmañcettha sabbāpi vedanā aniccato passitabbā, aniccadassanato pana sātisayaṃ virāganimittaṃ dukkhadassananti imamatthaṃ dassento satthā‘‘ sukhā, bhikkhave, vedanā dukkhato daṭṭhabbā, dukkhā vedanā sallato daṭṭhabbā’’ ti āha. "
611613,124,930,72,82,1,81,9,"Atha vā yattha puthujjanā sukhābhinivesino, tattha nibbedajananatthaṃ tathā vuttaṃ. "
611614,124,930,83,87,1,46,4,Tenassā saṅkhāradukkhatāya dukkhabhāvo dassito. 
611615,124,930,88,149,1,309,39,"Yadaniccaṃ, taṃ dukkhanti vipariṇāmadukkhatāya‘‘ sukhā, bhikkhave, vedanā dukkhato daṭṭhabbā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ sukhāpi tāva edisī, dukkhā nu kho kīdisī’’ ti cintentānaṃ dukkhadukkhatāya‘‘ dukkhā vedanā sallato daṭṭhabbā’’ ti āha, itarā pana saṅkhāradukkhatāya eva dukkhāti dassento‘‘ adukkhamasukhā vedanā aniccato daṭṭhabbā’’ ti avoca. "
611616,124,931,2,17,1,82,11,Ettha ca‘‘ sukhā vedanā dukkhato daṭṭhabbā’’ ti etena rāgassa samugghātanūpāyo dassito. 
611617,124,931,18,22,1,35,4,Sukhavedanāya hi rāgānusayo anuseti.
611618,124,931,23,36,1,73,9,‘‘ Dukkhā vedanā sallato daṭṭhabbā’’ ti etena dosassa samugghātanūpāyo dassito. 
611619,124,931,37,41,1,39,4,Dukkhavedanāya hi paṭighānusayo anuseti.
611620,124,931,42,55,1,82,9,‘‘ Adukkhamasukhā vedanā aniccato daṭṭhabbā’’ ti etena mohassa samugghātanūpāyo dassito. 
611621,124,931,56,60,1,46,4,Adukkhamasukhavedanāya hi avijjānusayo anuseti. 
611622,124,932,2,15,1,115,10,"Tathā paṭhamena taṇhāsaṃkilesassa pahānaṃ dassitaṃ tassa sukhassādahetukattā, dutiyena duccaritasaṃkilesassa pahānaṃ. "
611623,124,932,16,23,1,75,7,Yathābhūtañhi dukkhaṃ aparijānantā tassa pariharaṇatthaṃ duccaritaṃ caranti. 
611624,124,932,24,36,1,154,11,"Tatiyena diṭṭhisaṃkilesassa pahānaṃ aniccato passantassa diṭṭhisaṃkilesābhāvato avijjānimittattā diṭṭhisaṃkilesassa, avijjānimittañca adukkhamasukhā vedanā. "
611625,124,932,37,46,1,96,7,"Paṭhamena vā vipariṇāmadukkhapariññā, dutiyena dukkhadukkhapariññā, tatiyena saṅkhāradukkhapariññā. "
611626,124,932,47,56,1,96,7,"Paṭhamena vā iṭṭhārammaṇapariññā, dutiyena aniṭṭhārammaṇapariññā, tatiyena majjhattārammaṇapariññā. "
611627,124,932,57,63,1,65,6,Virattesu hi tadārammaṇadhammesu ārammaṇānipi virattāneva hontīti. 
611628,124,932,64,84,1,248,18,"Paṭhamena vā rāgappahānaparikittanena dukkhānupassanāya appaṇihitavimokkho dīpito hoti, dutiyena dosappahānaparikittanena aniccānupassanāya animittavimokkho, tatiyena mohappahānaparikittanena anattānupassanāya suññatavimokkho dīpito hotīti veditabbaṃ. "
611629,124,933,2,8,1,20,4,"{Yato}ti yadā, yasmā vā. "
611630,124,933,9,15,1,39,5,{Ariyo}ti kilesehi ārakā ṭhito parisuddho. 
611631,124,933,16,24,1,71,7,{Sammaddaso}ti sabbāsaṃ vedanānaṃ catunnampi vā saccānaṃ aviparītadassāvī. 
611632,124,933,25,35,1,83,9,"Acchecchi taṇhan ti vedanāmūlakaṃ taṇhaṃ aggamaggena chindi, anavasesato samucchindi. "
611633,124,933,36,44,1,71,7,"Vivattayi saṃyojanan ti dasavidhaṃ saṃyojanaṃ parivattayi, nimmūlamakāsi. "
611634,124,933,45,49,1,23,3,{Sammā}ti hetunā kāraṇena. 
611635,124,933,50,57,1,59,5,"{Mānābhisamayā}ti mānassa dassanābhisamayā, pahānābhisamayā vā. "
