611914,124,1004,26,36,1,99,10,Khayasmin ti anavasesakilesānaṃ khepanato khayasaṅkhāte aggamagge ñāṇaṃ paṭhamaṃ pureyeva uppajjati. 
611915,124,1004,37,46,1,66,8,Tato aññā {anantarā}ti tato maggañāṇato anantarā arahattaṃ uppajjati. 
611916,124,1004,47,73,1,323,24,Atha vā {ujumaggānusārino}ti līnuddhaccapatiṭṭhānāyūhanādike vajjetvā samathavipassanaṃ yuganaddhaṃ katvā bhāvanāvasena pavattaṃ pubbabhāgamaggaṃ anussarantassa anugacchantassa paṭipajjantassa gotrabhuñāṇānantaraṃ diṭṭhekaṭṭhānaṃ kilesānaṃ khepanato khayasmiṃ sotāpattimagge paṭhamaṃ ñāṇaṃ anaññātaññassāmītindriyaṃ uppajjati. 
