613508,124,1444,30,49,1,143,15,"Bahiddhā cassa viññāṇaṃ avikkhittaṃ avisaṭan ti bahiddhā rūpādiārammaṇe uppajjanakavikkhepābhāvato avikkhittaṃ samāhitaṃ, tato eva avisaṭaṃ siyā . "
613509,124,1444,50,93,1,414,39,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– bhikkhave, yena yena pakārena imassa āraddhavipassakassa bhikkhuno upaparikkhato saṅkhāre sammasantassa pubbe samāhitākārasallakkhaṇavasena samathanimittaṃ gahetvā sakkaccaṃ nirantaraṃ sammasanañāṇaṃ pavattentassa attano vipassanācittaṃ kammaṭṭhānato bahiddhā rūpādiārammaṇe uppajjanakaṃ na siyā, accāraddhavīriyatāya uddhaccapakkhiyaṃ na siyā, tena tena pakārena bhikkhu upaparikkheyya parituleyyāti. "
