614404,124,1638,36,69,1,247,28,"Atha vā yo kāmavitakkabahulo puggalo kalyāṇamittassa vasena pabbajjaṃ sīlavisodhanaṃ jhānādīnaṃ pubbabhāgapaṭipattiṃ vā paṭipajjanto kicchena kasirena assumukho rodamāno taṃ vitakkaṃ vikkhambheti, taṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ‘‘ sahāpi dukkhena jaheyya kāme’’ ti. "
