614456,124,1650,2,12,1,79,6,111. Dvādasame {sampannasīlā}ti ettha tividhaṃ sampannaṃ paripuṇṇasamaṅgīmadhuravasena. 
614457,124,1650,13,14,1,4,1,Tesu–
614458,124,1651,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Sampannaṃ sālikedāraṃ, suvā bhuñjanti kosiya; "
614459,124,1652,2,22,1,43,7,"Paṭivedemi te brahme, na ne vāretumussahe’’ ti.( jā.1.14.1)– "
614460,124,1653,2,5,1,33,3,Ettha paripuṇṇattho sampannasaddo.
614461,124,1653,6,29,1,125,13,‘‘ Iminā pātimokkhasaṃvarena upeto hoti samupeto upagato samupagato sampanno samannāgato’’ ti( vibha.511) ettha samaṅgibhāvattho sampannasaddo .
614462,124,1653,30,57,1,131,13,"‘‘ Imissā, bhante, mahāpathaviyā heṭṭhimatalaṃ sampannaṃ– seyyathāpi khuddamadhuṃ anīlakaṃ, evamassādan’’ ti( pārā.17) ettha madhurattho sampannasaddo. "
614463,124,1653,58,75,1,143,14,"Idha pana paripuṇṇatthepi samaṅgibhāvepi vaṭṭati, tasmā {sampannasīlā}ti paripuṇṇasīlā hutvātipi, sīlasamaṅgino hutvātipi evamettha attho veditabbo. "
614464,124,1654,2,17,1,97,11,Tattha ‘‘ paripuṇṇasīlā’’ ti iminā atthena khettadosavigamena khettapāripūri viya paripuṇṇaṃ nāma hoti. 
614465,124,1654,18,31,1,89,9,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ khettadosavigamena khettapāripūri viya sīladosavigamena sīlapāripūri vuttā’’ ti.
614466,124,1654,32,49,1,111,13,‘‘ Sīlasamaṅgino’’ ti iminā pana atthena sīlena samaṅgībhūtā samodhānagatā samannāgatā hutvā viharathāti vuttaṃ hoti. 
614467,124,1654,50,61,1,108,10,"Tattha dvīhi kāraṇehi sampannasīlatā hoti sīlavipattiyā ādīnavadassanena, sīlasampattiyā ānisaṃsadassanena ca. "
614468,124,1654,62,73,1,49,4,Tadubhayampi visuddhimagge( visuddhi.1.20-21) vuttanayena veditabbaṃ. 
614469,124,1654,74,102,1,178,19,"Tattha‘‘ sampannasīlā’’ ti ettāvatā kira bhagavā catupārisuddhisīlaṃ uddisitvā‘‘ pātimokkhasaṃvarasaṃvutā’’ ti iminā jeṭṭhakasīlaṃ dassetītiādinā ettha yaṃ vattabbaṃ, taṃ heṭṭhā vuttameva. "
614470,124,1654,103,119,1,123,15,"Kimassa uttari karaṇīyan ti evaṃ sampannasīlānaṃ viharataṃ tumhākaṃ kinti siyā uttari kātabbaṃ, paṭipajjitabbanti ceti attho. "
614471,124,1655,2,47,1,351,32,"Evaṃ ‘‘ sampannasīlā, bhikkhave, viharathā’’ tiādinā sampādanūpāyena saddhiṃ sīlasampadāya bhikkhū niyojento anekapuggalādhiṭṭhānaṃ katvā desanaṃ ārabhitvā idāni yasmā ekapuggalādhiṭṭhānavasena pavattitāpi bhagavato desanā anekapuggalādhiṭṭhānāva hoti sabbasādhāraṇattā, tasmā taṃ ekapuggalādhiṭṭhānavasena dassento‘‘ carato cepi, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno’’ tiādimāha. "
614472,124,1656,2,10,1,93,7,"Tattha abhijjhāyati etāyāti abhijjhā, parabhaṇḍābhijjhāyanalakkhaṇassa lobhassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
614473,124,1656,11,28,1,141,12,"Byāpajjati pūtibhavati cittaṃ etenāti byāpādo,‘‘ anatthaṃ me acarī’’ tiādinayappavattassa ekūnavīsatiāghātavatthuvisayassa dosassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
614474,124,1656,29,36,1,36,4,Ubhinnampi‘‘ tattha katamo kāmacchando? 
614475,124,1656,37,110,1,336,36,"Yo kāmesu kāmacchando kāmasneho kāmapipāsā kāmapariḷāho kāmamucchā kāmajjhosānan’’ ti ( dha. sa.1159), tathā‘‘ lobho lubbhanā lubbhitattaṃ sārāgo sārajjanā sārajjitattaṃ abhijjhā lobho akusalamūlan’’ tiādinā( dha. sa.391),‘‘ doso dussanā dussitattaṃ byāpatti byāpajjanā byāpajjitattaṃ virodho paṭivirodho caṇḍikkaṃ asuropo anattamanatā cittassā’’ tiādinā( dha. sa.418,1237) ca vitthāro veditabbo. "
614476,124,1656,111,126,1,84,12,"Vigato {hotī}ti ayañca abhijjhā, ayañca byāpādo vigato hoti apagato, pahīno hotīti attho. "
614477,124,1656,127,135,1,78,8,Ettāvatā kāmacchandanīvaraṇassa ca byāpādanīvaraṇassa ca pahānaṃ dassitaṃ hoti. 
614478,124,1657,2,6,1,36,4,Thinamiddhan ti thinañceva middhañca. 
614479,124,1657,7,23,1,142,13,"Tesu cittassa akammaññatā thinaṃ, ālasiyassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ, vedanādīnaṃ tiṇṇaṃ khandhānaṃ akammaññatā middhaṃ, pacalāyikabhāvassetaṃ adhivacanaṃ. "
614480,124,1657,24,30,1,32,4,Ubhinnampi‘‘ tattha katamaṃ thinaṃ? 
614481,124,1657,31,37,1,50,6,Yā cittassa akallatā akammaññatā olīyanā sallīyanā. 
614482,124,1657,38,41,1,22,3,Tattha katamaṃ middhaṃ? 
614483,124,1657,42,61,1,83,10,Yā kāyassa akallatā akammaññatā onāho pariyonāho’’ tiādinā( dha. sa.1162-1163) nayena vitthāro veditabbo. 
614484,124,1658,2,6,1,46,4,Uddhaccakukkuccan ti uddhaccañceva kukkuccañca. 
614485,124,1658,7,19,1,108,11,"Tattha uddhaccaṃ nāma cittassa uddhatākāro, kukkuccaṃ nāma akatakalyāṇassa katapāpassa tappaccayā vippaṭisāro. "
614486,124,1658,20,26,1,35,4,Ubhinnampi‘‘ tattha katamaṃ uddhaccaṃ? 
614487,124,1658,27,46,1,86,10,Yaṃ cittassa uddhaccaṃ avūpasamo cetaso vikkhepo bhantattaṃ cittassā’’ tiādinā( dha. sa.1165) vitthāro.
614488,124,1658,47,59,1,57,8,"‘‘ Akataṃ vata me kalyāṇaṃ, akataṃ kusalaṃ, akataṃ bhīruttānaṃ; "
614489,124,1658,60,86,1,71,9,"kataṃ pāpaṃ, kataṃ luddaṃ, kataṃ kibbisan’’ tiādinā( ma. ni.3.248; netti.120) pavattiākāro veditabbo. "
614490,124,1659,2,6,1,31,3,{Vicikicchā}ti buddhādīsu saṃsayo. 
614491,124,1659,7,31,1,98,11,"Tassā‘‘ satthari kaṅkhati vicikicchati, nādhimuccati na sampasīdatī’’ tiādinā( vibha.915),‘‘ tattha katamā vicikicchā? "
614492,124,1659,32,62,1,205,21,Yā kaṅkhā kaṅkhāyanā kaṅkhāyitattaṃ vimati vicikicchā dveḷhakaṃ dvedhāpatho saṃsayo anekaṃsaggāho āsappanā parisappanā apariyogāhanā chambhitattaṃ cittassa manovilekho’’ tiādinā( dha. sa.1008) ca nayena vitthāro veditabbo. 
614493,124,1660,2,12,1,95,10,Ettha ca abhijjhābyāpādādīnaṃ vigamavasena ca pahānavasena ca tesaṃ vikkhambhanameva veditabbaṃ. 
614494,124,1660,13,16,1,19,3,Yaṃ sandhāya vuttaṃ–
614495,124,1661,2,17,1,86,11,"‘ ‘ So abhijjhaṃ loke pahāya vigatābhijjhena cetasā viharati, abhijjhāya cittaṃ parisodheti. "
614496,124,1661,18,26,1,78,7,"Byāpādapadosaṃ pahāya abyāpannacitto viharati, byāpādapadosā cittaṃ parisodheti. "
614497,124,1661,27,39,1,103,10,"Thinamiddhaṃ pahāya vigatathinamiddho viharati ālokasaññī sato sampajāno, thinamiddhā cittaṃ parisodheti. "
614498,124,1661,40,49,1,103,9,Uddhaccakukkuccaṃ pahāya anuddhato viharati ajjhattaṃ upasantacitto uddhaccakukkuccā cittaṃ parisodheti. 
614499,124,1661,50,69,1,109,11,"Vicikicchaṃ pahāya tiṇṇavicikiccho viharati akathaṃkathī kusalesu dhammesu, vicikicchāya cittaṃ parisodhetī’’ ti( vibha.508). "
614500,124,1662,2,10,1,52,7,"Tattha yathā nīvaraṇānaṃ pahānaṃ hoti, taṃ veditabbaṃ. "
614501,124,1662,11,15,1,27,4,Kathañca nesaṃ pahānaṃ hoti? 
614502,124,1662,16,26,1,109,9,"Kāmacchandassa tāva asubhanimitte yonisomanasikārena pahānaṃ hoti, subhanimitte ayonisomanasikārenassa uppatti. "
614503,124,1662,27,29,1,14,2,Tenāha bhagavā–
614504,124,1663,2,9,1,29,4,"‘ ‘ Atthi, bhikkhave, subhanimittaṃ. "
614505,124,1663,10,35,1,140,13,"Tattha ayonisomanasikārabahulīkāro ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā kāmacchandassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā kāmacchandassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāyā’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.232). "
614506,124,1664,2,12,1,128,10,Evaṃ subhanimitte ayonisomanasikārena uppajjantassa kāmacchandassa tappaṭipakkhato asubhanimitte yonisomanasikārena pahānaṃ hoti. 
614507,124,1664,13,41,1,199,22,"Tattha asubhanimittaṃ nāma asubhampi asubhārammaṇampi, yonisomanasikāro nāma upāyamanasikāro, pathamanasikāro, anicce aniccanti vā, dukkhe dukkhanti vā, anattani anattāti vā, asubhe asubhanti vā manasikāro. "
614508,124,1664,42,48,1,51,6,Taṃ tattha bahulaṃ pavattayato kāmacchando pahīyati. 
614509,124,1664,49,51,1,14,2,Tenāha bhagavā–
614510,124,1665,2,9,1,30,4,"‘ ‘ Atthi, bhikkhave, asubhanimittaṃ. "
614511,124,1665,10,35,1,126,12,"Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro– ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā kāmacchandassa anuppādāya, uppannassa vā kāmacchandassa pahānāyā’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.232). "
614512,124,1666,2,23,1,168,15,"Apica cha dhammā kāmacchandassa pahānāya saṃvattanti– asubhanimittassa uggaho, asubhabhāvanānuyogo, indriyesu guttadvāratā, bhojane mattaññutā, kalyāṇamittatā, sappāyakathāti. "
614513,124,1666,24,46,1,195,18,"Dasavidhañhi asubhanimittaṃ uggaṇhantassapi kāmacchando pahīyati, bhāventassapi , indriyesu pihitadvārassapi catunnaṃ pañcannaṃ ālopānaṃ okāse sati udakaṃ pivitvā yāpanasīlatāya bhojane mattaññunopi. "
614514,124,1666,47,49,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
614515,124,1667,2,12,1,39,7,"‘ ‘ Cattāro pañca ālope, abhutvā udakaṃ pive; "
614516,124,1668,2,16,1,44,5,"Alaṃ phāsuvihārāya, pahitattassa bhikkhuno’’ ti.( theragā.983); "
614517,124,1669,2,11,1,137,8,"Asubhakammikatissattherasadise kalyāṇamitte sevantassapi kāmacchando pahīyati, ṭhānanisajjādīsu dasaasubhanissitasappāyakathāyapi pahīyati. "
614518,124,1669,12,24,1,61,8,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ cha dhammā kāmacchandassa pahānāya saṃvattantī’’ ti. 
614519,124,1670,2,7,1,57,5,Paṭighanimitte āyonisomanasikārena byāpādassa uppādo hoti. 
614520,124,1670,8,14,1,67,5,"Tattha paṭighampi paṭighanimittaṃ, paṭighārammaṇampi paṭighanimittaṃ. "
614521,124,1670,15,19,1,43,4,Ayonisomanasikāro sabbattha ekalakkhaṇo eva. 
614522,124,1670,20,27,1,56,7,Taṃ tasmiṃ nimitte bahulaṃ pavattayato byāpādo uppajjati. 
614523,124,1670,28,30,1,14,2,Tenāha bhagavā–
614524,124,1671,2,9,1,31,4,"‘ ‘ Atthi, bhikkhave, paṭighanimittaṃ. "
614525,124,1671,10,36,1,132,13,"Tattha ayonisomanasikārabahulīkāro– ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā byāpādassa uppādāya, uppannassa vā byāpādassa bhiyyobhāvāya vepullāyā’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.232). "
614526,124,1672,2,8,1,61,6,Mettāya pana cetovimuttiyā yonisomanasikārenassa pahānaṃ hoti. 
614527,124,1672,9,29,1,77,11,"Tattha‘‘ mettā’’ ti vutte appanāpi upacāropi vaṭṭati,‘‘ cetovimuttī’’ ti pana appanāva. "
614528,124,1672,30,32,1,32,2,Yonisomanasikāro vuttalakkhaṇova. 
614529,124,1672,33,39,1,47,6,Taṃ tattha bahulaṃ pavattayato byāpādo pahīyati. 
614530,124,1672,40,42,1,14,2,Tenāha bhagavā–
614531,124,1673,2,9,1,32,4,"‘ ‘ Atthi, bhikkhave, mettācetovimutti. "
614532,124,1673,10,33,1,118,12,Tattha yonisomanasikārabahulīkāro ayamāhāro anuppannassa vā byāpādassa anuppādāya uppannassa vā byāpādassa pahānāyā’’ ti( saṃ. ni.5.232). 
614533,124,1674,2,21,1,161,13,"Apica cha dhammā byāpādassa pahānāya saṃvattanti– mettānimittassa uggaho, mettābhāvanā, kammassakatāpaccavekkhaṇā, paṭisaṅkhānabahulatā, kalyāṇamittatā, sappāyakathāti. "
614534,124,1674,22,70,1,392,39,"Odhisakānodhisakadisāpharaṇānañhi aññataravasena mettaṃ uggaṇhantassapi byāpādo pahīyati, odhiso anodhiso disāpharaṇavasena mettaṃ bhāventassapi byāpādo pahīyati,‘‘ tvaṃ etassa kuddho kiṃ karissasi, kimassa sīlādīni vināsetuṃ sakkhissasi nanu tvaṃ attano kammena āgantvā attano kammeneva gamissasi, parassa kujjhanaṃ nāma vītaccikaṅgāratattaayasalākagūthādīni gahetvā paraṃ paharitukāmatā viya hoti. "
614535,124,1674,71,128,1,470,49,"Esopi tava kuddho kiṃ karissati, kiṃ te sīlādīni vināsetuṃ sakkhissati esa attano kammena āgantvā attano kammeneva gamissati, appaṭicchitapaheṇakaṃ viya, paṭivātaṃ khittarajomuṭṭhi viya ca etasseva esa kodho matthake patissatī’’ ti evaṃ attano ca parassa cāti ubhayesaṃ kammassakataṃ paccavekkhatopi, paccavekkhitvā paṭisaṅkhāne ṭhitassapi, assaguttattherasadise mettābhāvanārate kalyāṇamitte sevantassāpi byāpādo pahīyati, ṭhānanisajjādīsu mettānissitasappāyakathāyapi pahīyati. "
614536,124,1674,129,141,1,57,8,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ cha dhammā byāpādassa pahānāya saṃvattantī’’ ti. 
614537,124,1675,2,7,1,57,5,Aratiādīsu ayonisomanasikārena thinamiddhassa uppādo hoti. 
614538,124,1675,8,30,1,161,18,"Arati nāma ukkaṇṭhitatā, tandī nāma kāyālasiyaṃ, vijambhitā nāma kāyavinamanā, bhattasammado nāma bhattamucchā bhattapariḷāho, cetaso līnattaṃ nāma cittassa līnākāro. "
614539,124,1675,31,38,1,78,7,Imesu aratiādīsu ayonisomanasikāraṃ bahulaṃ pavattayato thinamiddhaṃ uppajjati. 
