615606,125,196,2,49,1,228,31,34. Atha bhagavā‘‘ māro ayaṃ pāpimā imesaṃ antarāyāya āgato’’ ti viditvā phalena phalaṃ pātento viya tāyeva mārenābhatāya upamāya māravādaṃ bhindanto tameva gāthaṃ parivattetvā‘‘ upadhi sokavatthū’’ ti dassento āha‘‘ socati puttehi puttimā’’ ti. 
