615630,125,199,2,4,1,24,2,3 . Khaggavisāṇasuttavaṇṇanā 
615631,125,200,2,8,1,36,3,Sabbesu {bhūtesū}ti khaggavisāṇasuttaṃ. 
615632,125,200,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
615633,125,200,12,24,1,94,8,"Sabbasuttānaṃ catubbidhā uppatti– attajjhāsayato, parajjhāsayato, aṭṭhuppattito, pucchāvasito cāti. "
615634,125,200,25,37,1,139,9,"Dvayatānupassanādīnañhi attajjhāsayato uppatti, mettasuttādīnaṃ parajjhāsayato, uragasuttādīnaṃ aṭṭhuppattito, dhammikasuttādīnaṃ pucchāvasito. "
615635,125,200,38,43,1,58,5,Tattha khaggavisāṇasuttassa avisesena pucchāvasito uppatti. 
615636,125,200,44,71,1,213,24,"Visesena pana yasmā ettha kāci gāthā tena tena paccekasambuddhena puṭṭhena vuttā, kāci apuṭṭhena attanā adhigatamagganayānurūpaṃ udānaṃyeva udānentena, tasmā kāyaci gāthāya pucchāvasito, kāyaci attajjhāsayato uppatti. "
615637,125,201,2,21,1,119,16,"Tattha yā ayaṃ avisesena pucchāvasito uppatti, sā ādito pabhuti evaṃ veditabbā– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
615638,125,201,22,32,1,86,10,Atha kho āyasmato ānandassa rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko udapādi–
615639,125,201,33,41,1,43,6,‘‘ buddhānaṃ patthanā ca abhinīhāro ca dissati; 
615640,125,201,42,48,1,43,5,"tathā sāvakānaṃ, paccekabuddhānaṃ na dissati; "
615641,125,201,49,56,1,50,5,yaṃnūnāhaṃ bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā puccheyyan’’ ti. 
615642,125,201,57,65,1,80,8,So paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā yathākkamena etamatthaṃ pucchi. 
615643,125,201,66,70,1,44,4,Athassa bhagavā pubbayogāvacarasuttaṃ abhāsi–
615644,125,202,2,15,1,82,10,"‘ ‘ Pañcime, ānanda, ānisaṃsā pubbayogāvacare diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacceva aññaṃ ārādheti. "
615645,125,202,16,28,1,79,11,"No ce diṭṭheva dhamme paṭikacceva aññaṃ ārādheti, atha maraṇakāle aññaṃ ārādheti. "
615646,125,202,29,55,1,159,21,"No ce maraṇakāle aññaṃ ārādheti, atha devaputto samāno aññaṃ ārādheti, atha buddhānaṃ sammukhībhāve khippābhiñño hoti, atha pacchime kāle paccekasambuddho hotī’’ ti– "
