616100,125,267,11,41,1,230,25,"Ayaṃ paccekabodhisatto purimagāthāya vuttanayeneva uppajjitvā bārāṇasiyaṃ rajjaṃ kārento paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ nibbattetvā‘‘ kiṃ samaṇadhammo varo, rajjaṃ varan’’ ti vīmaṃsitvā catunnaṃ amaccānaṃ hatthe rajjaṃ niyyātetvā samaṇadhammaṃ karoti. "
616101,125,267,42,56,1,74,10,Amaccā‘‘ dhammena samena karothā’’ ti vuttāpi lañjaṃ gahetvā adhammena karonti. 
616102,125,267,57,66,1,74,9,Te lañjaṃ gahetvā sāmike parājentā ekadā aññataraṃ rājavallabhaṃ parājesuṃ. 
