616352,125,314,110,124,1,48,9,"‘‘ Bhante, tumhākaṃ taṃ bhayaṃ kiṃ kāraṇā na hotī’’ ti?"
616353,125,314,125,157,1,152,22,"‘‘ Mayañhi, mahārāja, mettaṃ bhāvema, karuṇaṃ bhāvema, muditaṃ bhāvema, upekkhaṃ bhāvema, tena no taṃ bhayaṃ na hotī’’ ti vatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā attano vasatiṃ agamaṃsu. "
616354,125,315,2,28,1,150,20,"Tato rājā cintesi‘‘ ime samaṇā mettādibhāvanāya bhayaṃ na hotīti bhaṇanti, brāhmaṇā pana anekasahassapāṇavadhaṃ vaṇṇayanti, kesaṃ nu kho vacanaṃ saccan’’ ti. "
