616853,125,403,99,125,1,177,20,"Tato so‘‘ kudāssu nāmāhampi evaṃ bahussuto bhavissāmī’’ ti tathārūpaṃ bahussutabhāvaṃ patthento rajjaṃ pahāya pabbajitvā, vipassanto paccekabodhiṃ sacchikatvā, imaṃ udānagāthaṃ abhāsi–"
