616856,125,406,2,21,1,167,16,"Tatthāyaṃ saṅkhepattho– bahussutan ti duvidho bahussuto tīsu piṭakesu atthato nikhilo pariyattibahussuto ca, maggaphalavijjābhiññānaṃ paṭividdhattā paṭivedhabahussuto ca. "
