616912,125,418,48,65,1,117,12,Tā nāṭakitthiyo‘‘ rājānaṃ ramāpessāmā’’ ti sakkassa devānamindassa accharāyo viya atimanoharaṃ naccagītavāditaṃ payojesuṃ. 
