616976,125,433,2,9,1,23,3,64. {Ohārayitvā}ti kā uppatti? 
616977,125,433,10,21,1,99,11,Bārāṇasiyaṃ kira ayaṃ aññopi cātumāsikabrahmadatto nāma rājā catumāse catumāse uyyānakīḷaṃ gacchati. 
616978,125,433,22,40,1,168,17,So ekadivasaṃ gimhānaṃ majjhime māse uyyānaṃ pavisanto uyyānadvāre pattasañchannaṃ pupphālaṅkataviṭapaṃ pāricchattakakoviḷāraṃ disvā ekaṃ pupphaṃ gahetvā uyyānaṃ pāvisi. 
616979,125,433,41,58,1,98,13,Tato‘‘ raññā aggapupphaṃ gahitan’’ ti aññataropi amacco hatthikkhandhe ṭhito eva ekaṃ pupphaṃ aggahesi. 
616980,125,433,59,64,1,39,5,Eteneva upāyena sabbo balakāyo aggahesi. 
616981,125,433,65,70,1,37,4,Pupphaṃ anassādentā pattampi gaṇhiṃsu. 
616982,125,433,71,76,1,45,5,So rukkho nippattapuppho khandhamattova ahosi. 
616983,125,433,77,108,1,237,25,"Taṃ rājā sāyanhasamaye uyyānā nikkhamanto disvā‘‘ kiṃ kato ayaṃ rukkho, mama āgamanavelāyaṃ maṇivaṇṇasākhantaresu pavāḷasadisapupphālaṅkato ahosi, idāni nippattapuppho jāto’’ ti cintento tassevāvidūre apupphitaṃ rukkhaṃ sañchannapalāsaṃ addasa. "
616984,125,433,109,112,1,21,3,Disvā cassa etadahosi–
616985,125,433,113,132,1,134,15,"‘‘ ayaṃ rukkho pupphabharitasākhattā bahujanassa lobhanīyo ahosi, tena muhutteneva byasanaṃ patto, ayaṃ panañño alobhanīyattā tatheva ṭhito. "
616986,125,433,133,145,1,94,10,"Idampi rajjaṃ pupphitarukkho viya lobhanīyaṃ, bhikkhubhāvo pana apupphitarukkho viya alobhanīyo. "
616987,125,433,146,169,1,149,19,"Tasmā yāva idampi ayaṃ rukkho viya na viluppati, tāva ayamañño sañchannapatto yathā pāricchattako, evaṃ kāsāvena parisañchannena hutvā pabbajitabban’’ ti. "
616988,125,433,170,180,1,88,10,So rajjaṃ pahāya pabbajitvā vipassanto paccekabodhiṃ sacchikatvā imaṃ udānagāthaṃ abhāsi–
616989,125,434,2,10,1,57,6,"‘ ‘ Ohārayitvā gihibyañjanāni, sañchannapatto yathā pārichatto; "
616990,125,435,2,11,1,58,6,"Kāsāyavattho abhinikkhamitvā, eko care khaggavisāṇakappo’’ ti. "
616991,125,436,2,14,1,114,11,Tattha kāsāyavattho {abhinikkhamitvā}ti imassa pādassa gehā abhinikkhamitvā kāsāyavattho hutvāti evamattho veditabbo. 
616992,125,436,15,21,1,52,6,Sesaṃ vuttanayeneva sakkā jānitunti na vitthāritanti. 
616993,125,437,2,4,1,33,2,Pāricchattakagāthāvaṇṇanā samattā. 
616994,125,438,2,5,1,21,3,Tatiyo vaggo niṭṭhito. 
616995,125,439,2,9,1,19,3,65. {Rasesū}ti kā uppatti? 
616996,125,439,10,18,1,86,8,Aññataro kira bārāṇasirājā uyyāne amaccaputtehi parivuto silāpaṭṭapokkharaṇiyaṃ kīḷati. 
616997,125,439,19,31,1,100,11,Tassa sūdo sabbamaṃsānaṃ rasaṃ gahetvā atīva susaṅkhataṃ amatakappaṃ antarabhattaṃ pacitvā upanāmesi. 
616998,125,439,32,40,1,59,8,So tattha gedhamāpanno kassaci kiñci adatvā attanāva bhuñji. 
616999,125,439,41,48,1,55,7,Udakakīḷato ca ativikāle nikkhanto sīghaṃ sīghaṃ bhuñji. 
617000,125,439,49,58,1,47,8,"Yehi saddhiṃ pubbe bhuñjati, na tesaṃ kañci sari. "
617001,125,439,59,79,1,122,15,"Atha pacchā paṭisaṅkhānaṃ uppādetvā‘‘ aho, mayā pāpaṃ kataṃ, yvāhaṃ rasataṇhāya abhibhūto sabbajanaṃ visaritvā ekakova bhuñjiṃ. "
617002,125,439,80,99,1,175,17,Handa rasataṇhaṃ niggaṇhāmī’’ ti rajjaṃ pahāya pabbajitvā vipassanto paccekabodhiṃ sacchikatvā attano purimapaṭipattiṃ garahanto tappaṭipakkhaguṇadīpikaṃ imaṃ udānagāthaṃ abhāsi–
617003,125,440,2,11,1,50,7,"‘ ‘ Rasesu gedhaṃ akaraṃ alolo, anaññaposī sapadānacārī; "
617004,125,441,2,12,1,57,7,"Kule kule appaṭibaddhacitto, eko care khaggavisāṇakappo’’ ti. "
617005,125,442,2,7,1,81,4,Tattha {rasesū}ti ambilamadhuratittakakaṭukaloṇikakhārikakasāvādibhedesu sāyanīyesu. 
617006,125,442,8,18,1,66,9,"Gedhaṃ akaran ti giddhiṃ akaronto, taṇhaṃ anuppādentoti vuttaṃ hoti. "
617007,125,442,19,34,1,66,9,"{Alolo}ti‘‘ idaṃ sāyissāmi, idaṃ sāyissāmī’’ ti evaṃ rasavisesesu anākulo. "
617008,125,442,35,44,1,94,6,"{Anaññaposī}ti posetabbakasaddhivihārikādivirahito , kāyasandhāraṇamattena santuṭṭhoti vuttaṃ hoti. "
617009,125,442,45,64,1,121,18,"Yathā vā pubbe uyyāne rasesu gedhakaraṇalolo hutvā aññaposī āsiṃ, evaṃ ahutvā yāya taṇhāya lolo hutvā rasesu gedhaṃ karoti. "
617010,125,442,65,75,1,94,10,Taṃ taṇhaṃ hitvā āyatiṃ taṇhāmūlakassa aññassa attabhāvassa anibbattanena anaññaposīti dasseti. 
617011,125,442,76,82,1,52,6,Atha vā atthabhañjanakaṭṭhena aññeti kilesā vuccanti. 
617012,125,442,83,88,1,45,5,Tesaṃ aposanena anaññaposīti ayampettha attho. 
617013,125,442,89,102,1,133,11,"{Sapadānacārī}ti avokkammacārī anupubbacārī, gharapaṭipāṭiṃ achaḍḍetvā aḍḍhakulañca daliddakulañca nirantaraṃ piṇḍāya pavisamānoti attho. "
617014,125,442,103,117,1,123,12,"Kule kule {appaṭibaddhacitto}ti khattiyakulādīsu yattha katthaci kilesavasena alaggacitto, candūpamo niccanavako hutvāti attho. "
617015,125,442,118,120,1,21,2,Sesaṃ vuttanayamevāti. 
