617043,125,452,28,31,1,37,3,Samathan ti catutthajjhānasamathameva. 
617044,125,452,32,43,1,150,10,"Visuddhan ti pañcanīvaraṇavitakkavicārapītisukhasaṅkhātehi navahi paccanīkadhammehi vimuttattā visuddhaṃ, niddhantasuvaṇṇamiva vigatūpakkilesanti attho. "
617045,125,453,2,16,1,143,12,"Ayaṃ pana yojanā– vipiṭṭhikatvāna sukhaṃ dukkhañca pubbeva paṭhamajjhānupacārabhūmiyaṃyeva dukkhaṃ, tatiyajjhānupacārabhūmiyaṃ sukhanti adhippāyo. "
617046,125,453,17,34,1,98,12,Puna ādito vuttaṃ cakāraṃ parato netvā‘‘ somanassaṃ domanassañca vipiṭṭhikatvāna pubbevā’’ ti adhikāro. 
617047,125,453,35,42,1,81,6,"Tena somanassaṃ catutthajjhānupacāre, domanassañca dutiyajjhānupacāreyevāti dīpeti. "
617048,125,453,43,48,1,41,5,Etāni hi etesaṃ pariyāyato pahānaṭṭhānāni. 
