617050,125,453,64,65,1,7,1,Yathāha–
617051,125,453,66,87,1,91,8,‘‘ paṭhamajjhānaṃ upasampajja viharati etthuppannaṃ dukkhindriyaṃ aparisesaṃ nirujjhatī’’ tiādi( saṃ. ni.5.510). 
