617572,125,543,2,49,1,207,29,"Soraccaṃ me pamocanan ti ettha yaṃ taṃ‘‘ kāyiko avītikkamo, vācasiko avītikkamo’’ ti, evaṃ sīlameva‘‘ soraccan’’ ti vuttaṃ, na taṃ idha adhippetaṃ, vuttameva etaṃ‘‘ kāyagutto’’ tiādinā nayena, arahattaphalaṃ pana adhippetaṃ. "
617573,125,543,50,62,1,56,8,Tampi hi sundare nibbāne ratabhāvato‘‘ soraccan’’ ti vuccati. 
