617861,125,592,32,97,1,433,54,"Tassattho– ete caturo samaṇe yathāvuttena lakkhaṇena paṭivijjhi aññāsi sacchākāsi yo gahaṭṭho khattiyo vā brāhmaṇo vā añño vā koci, imesaṃ catunnaṃ samaṇānaṃ lakkhaṇassavanamattena sutavā, tasseva lakkhaṇassa ariyānaṃ santike sutattā ariyasāvako, teyeva samaṇe‘‘ ayañca ayañca evaṃlakkhaṇo’’ ti pajānanamattena sappañño, yādiso ayaṃ pacchā vutto maggadūsī, itarepi sabbe netādisāti ñatvā iti disvā evaṃ pāpaṃ karontampi etaṃ pāpabhikkhuṃ disvā. "
