618149,125,662,75,76,1,7,1,Yathāha–
618150,125,663,2,12,1,54,7,"‘ ‘ Pañcime, bhikkhave, mahācorā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
618151,125,663,13,15,1,12,2,Katame pañca? 
618152,125,663,16,60,1,286,34,"Idha, bhikkhave, ekaccassa mahācorassa evaṃ hoti‘ kudāssu nāmāhaṃ satena vā sahassena vā parivuto gāmanigamarājadhānīsu āhiṇḍissāmi hananto, ghātento, chindanto, chedāpento, pacanto pācentoti, so aparena samayena satena vā sahassena vā parivuto gāmanigamarājadhānīsu āhiṇḍati hananto… pe… pācento. "
618153,125,663,61,101,1,220,27,"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, idhekaccassa pāpabhikkhuno evaṃ hoti‘ kudāssu nāmāhaṃ satena vā… pe… rājadhānīsu cārikaṃ carissāmi sakkato, garukato, mānito, pūjito, apacito, gahaṭṭhānañceva pabbajitānañca lābhī cīvara… pe… parikkhārānan’ ti. "
618154,125,663,102,119,1,113,14,So aparena samayena satena vā sahassena vā parivuto gāmanigamarājadhānīsu cārikaṃ carati sakkato… pe… parikkhārānaṃ. 
618155,125,663,120,129,1,59,7,"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo mahācoro santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ."
618156,125,664,2,26,1,140,16,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco pāpabhikkhu tathāgatappaveditaṃ dhammavinayaṃ pariyāpuṇitvā attano dahati, ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo… pe… lokasmiṃ."
618157,125,665,2,20,1,138,14,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco pāpabhikkhu suddhaṃ brahmacāriṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carantaṃ amūlakena abrahmacariyena anuddhaṃseti. "
618158,125,665,21,30,1,33,5,"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo… pe… lokasmiṃ."
618159,125,666,2,74,1,360,41,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco, pāpabhikkhu yāni tāni saṅghassa garubhaṇḍāni garuparikkhārāni, seyyathidaṃ– ārāmo, ārāmavatthu, vihāro, vihāravatthu, mañco, pīṭhaṃ, bhisi, bimbohanaṃ, lohakumbhī, lohabhāṇakaṃ, lohavārako, lohakaṭāhaṃ, vāsi, pharasu, kuṭhārī, kudālo, nikhādanaṃ, valli, veḷu, muñjaṃ, pabbajaṃ, tiṇaṃ, mattikā, dārubhaṇḍaṃ, mattikābhaṇḍaṃ, tehi gihiṃ saṅgaṇhāti upalāpeti. "
618160,125,666,75,84,1,35,5,"Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho… pe… lokasmiṃ."
618161,125,667,2,30,1,113,15,"‘ ‘ Sadevake, bhikkhave, loke… pe… sadevamanussāya ayaṃ aggo mahācoro, yo asantaṃ abhūtaṃ uttarimanussadhammaṃ ullapatī’’ ti( pārā.195). "
618162,125,668,2,7,1,52,5,Tattha lokiyacorā lokiyameva dhanadhaññādiṃ thenenti. 
618163,125,668,8,30,1,250,17,"Sāsane vuttacoresu paṭhamo tathārūpameva cīvarādipaccayamattaṃ, dutiyo pariyattidhammaṃ, tatiyo parassa brahmacariyaṃ, catuttho saṅghikagarubhaṇḍaṃ, pañcamo jhānasamādhisamāpattimaggaphalappabhedaṃ lokiyalokuttaraguṇadhanaṃ, lokiyañca cīvarādipaccayajātaṃ. "
618164,125,668,31,32,1,7,1,Yathāha–
618165,125,668,33,45,1,43,6,"‘‘ theyyāya vo, bhikkhave, raṭṭhapiṇḍo bhutto’’ ti. "
618166,125,668,46,62,1,77,11,"Tattha yvāyaṃ pañcamo mahācoro, taṃ sandhāyāha bhagavā‘‘ coro sabrahmake loke’’ ti. "
618167,125,668,63,112,1,248,30,"So hi‘‘ sadevake, bhikkhave, loke… pe… sadevamanussāya ayaṃ aggo mahācoro, yo asantaṃ abhūtaṃ uttarimanussadhammaṃ ullapatī’’ ti( pārā.195) evaṃ lokiyalokuttaradhanathenanato aggo mahācoroti vutto, tasmā taṃ idhāpi‘‘ sabrahmake loke’’ ti iminā ukkaṭṭhaparicchedena pakāsesi. "
