618189,125,673,14,28,1,79,12,{Mātaṅgo}ti evaṃnāmo {vissuto}ti evaṃ hīnāya jātiyā ca jīvikāya ca nāmena ca pākaṭo. 
618190,125,674,2,19,1,119,15,"{So}ti purimapadena sambandhitvā so mātaṅgo yasaṃ paramaṃ patto, abbhutaṃ uttamaṃ ativisiṭṭhaṃ yasaṃ kittiṃ pasaṃsaṃ patto. "
618191,125,674,20,29,1,83,8,"Yaṃ sudullabhan ti yaṃ uḷārakulūpapannenāpi dullabhaṃ, hīnakulūpapannena sudullabhaṃ. "
618192,125,674,30,56,1,209,24,"Evaṃ yasappattassa ca āgacchuṃ tassupaṭṭhānaṃ, khattiyā brāhmaṇā bahū, tassa mātaṅgassa pāricariyatthaṃ khattiyā ca brāhmaṇā ca aññe ca bahū vessasuddādayo jambudīpamanussā yebhuyyena upaṭṭhānaṃ āgamiṃsūti attho. "
618193,125,675,2,44,1,368,36,"Evaṃ upaṭṭhānasampanno so mātaṅgo vigatakilesarajattā virajaṃ, mahantehi buddhādīhi paṭipannattā mahāpathaṃ, brahmalokasaṅkhātaṃ devalokaṃ yāpetuṃ samatthattā devalokayānasaññitaṃ aṭṭhasamāpattiyānaṃ abhiruyha, tāya paṭipattiyā kāmarāgaṃ virājetvā, kāyassa bhedā brahmalokūpago ahu, sā tathā hīnāpi na naṃ jāti nivāresi brahmalokūpapattiyā, brahmalokūpapattitoti vuttaṃ hoti. "
618194,125,676,2,17,1,118,14,Ayaṃ panattho evaṃ veditabbo– atīte kira mahāpuriso tena tenupāyena sattahitaṃ karonto sopākajīvike caṇḍālakule uppajji. 
618195,125,676,18,35,1,116,14,"So nāmena mātaṅgo , rūpena duddasiko hutvā bahinagare cammakuṭikāya vasati, antonagare bhikkhaṃ caritvā jīvikaṃ kappeti. "
618196,125,676,36,46,1,87,9,Athekadivasaṃ tasmiṃ nagare surānakkhatte ghosite dhuttā yathāsakena parivārena kīḷanti. 
618197,125,676,47,75,1,290,23,Aññatarāpi brāhmaṇamahāsāladhītā pannarasasoḷasavassuddesikā devakaññā viya rūpena dassanīyā pāsādikā‘‘ attano kulavaṃsānurūpaṃ kīḷissāmī’’ ti pahūtaṃ khajjabhojjādikīḷanasambhāraṃ sakaṭesu āropetvā sabbasetavaḷavayuttaṃ yānamāruyha mahāparivārena uyyānabhūmiṃ gacchati {diṭṭhamaṅgalikā}ti nāmena. 
618198,125,676,76,94,1,104,13,"Sā kira‘‘ dussaṇṭhitaṃ rūpaṃ avamaṅgalan’’ ti daṭṭhuṃ na icchati, tenassā diṭṭhamaṅgalikātveva saṅkhā udapādi. "
618199,125,677,2,25,1,162,19,"Tadā so mātaṅgo kālasseva vuṭṭhāya paṭapilotikaṃ nivāsetvā, kaṃsatāḷaṃ hatthe bandhitvā, bhājanahattho nagaraṃ pavisati, manusse disvā dūrato eva kaṃsatāḷaṃ ākoṭento. "
618200,125,677,26,53,1,143,18,"Atha diṭṭhamaṅgalikā‘‘ ussaratha, ussarathā’’ ti purato purato hīnajanaṃ apanentehi purisehi nīyamānā nagaradvāramajjhe mātaṅgaṃ disvā‘‘ ko eso’’ ti āha. "
618201,125,677,54,56,1,21,2,Ahaṃ mātaṅgacaṇḍāloti. 
618202,125,677,57,70,1,56,9,Sā‘‘ īdisaṃ disvā gatānaṃ kuto vuḍḍhī’’ ti yānaṃ nivattāpesi. 
618203,125,677,71,112,1,215,28,"Manussā‘‘ yaṃ mayaṃ uyyānaṃ gantvā khajjabhojjādiṃ labheyyāma, tassa no mātaṅgena antarāyo kato’’ ti kupitā‘‘ gaṇhatha caṇḍālan’’ ti leḍḍūhi paharitvā‘‘ mato’’ ti pāde gahetvā ekamante chaḍḍetvā kacavarena paṭicchādetvā agamaṃsu. "
618204,125,677,113,119,1,44,6,So satiṃ paṭilabhitvā uṭṭhāya manusse pucchi–
618205,125,677,120,136,1,67,9,"‘‘ kiṃ, ayyā, dvāraṃ nāma sabbasādhāraṇaṃ, udāhu brāhmaṇānaṃyeva katan’’ ti? "
618206,125,677,137,139,1,14,2,Manussā āhaṃsu–
618207,125,677,140,147,1,22,3,‘‘ sabbesaṃ sādhāraṇan’’ ti.
618208,125,677,148,172,1,199,20,‘‘ Evaṃ sabbasādhāraṇadvārena pavisitvā bhikkhāhārena yāpentaṃ maṃ diṭṭhamaṅgalikāya manussā imaṃ anayabyasanaṃ pāpesun’’ ti rathikāya rathikaṃ āhiṇḍanto manussānaṃ ārocetvā brāhmaṇassa gharadvāre nipajji–
618209,125,677,173,182,1,44,5,‘‘ diṭṭhamaṅgalikaṃ aladdhā na vuṭṭhahissāmī’’ ti. 
618210,125,678,2,26,1,105,15,"Brāhmaṇo ‘‘ gharadvāre mātaṅgo nipanno’’ ti sutvā‘‘ tassa kākaṇikaṃ detha, telena aṅgaṃ makkhetvā gacchatū’’ ti āha. "
618211,125,678,27,43,1,69,10,"So taṃ na icchati,‘‘ diṭṭhamaṅgalikaṃ aladdhā na vuṭṭhahissāmi’’ cceva āha. "
618212,125,678,44,66,1,109,15,"Tato brāhmaṇo‘‘ dve kākaṇikāyo detha, kākaṇikāya pūvaṃ khādatu, kākaṇikāya telena aṅgaṃ makkhetvā gacchatū’’ ti āha. "
