618435,125,714,29,36,1,43,5,Tattha saṅkhepato sikkhattayaṃ karaṇīyan’’ ti. 
618436,125,714,37,47,1,77,9,"Atisaṅkhepadesitattā pana tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ kehici viññātaṃ, kehici na viññātaṃ. "
618437,125,714,48,83,1,183,27,"Tato yehi na viññātaṃ, tesaṃ viññāpanatthaṃ yaṃ visesato āraññakena bhikkhunā kātabbaṃ, taṃ vitthārento ‘‘ sakko ujū ca suhujū ca, suvaco cassa mudu anatimānī’’ ti imaṃ tāva upaḍḍhagāthaṃ āha. "
618438,125,715,2,5,1,15,3,Kiṃ vuttaṃ hoti? 
618439,125,715,6,52,1,421,43,"Santaṃ padaṃ abhisamecca viharitukāmo lokiyapaññāya vā taṃ abhisamecca tadadhigamāya paṭipajjamāno āraññako bhikkhu dutiyacatutthapadhāniyaṅgasamannāgamena kāye ca jīvite ca anapekkho hutvā saccapaṭivedhāya paṭipajjituṃ sakko assa, tathā kasiṇaparikammavattasamādānādīsu, attano pattacīvarapaṭisaṅkharaṇādīsu ca yāni tāni sabrahmacārīnaṃ uccāvacāni kiṃ karaṇīyāni, tesu aññesu ca evarūpesu sakko assa dakkho analaso samattho. "
618440,125,715,53,59,1,57,6,Sakko hontopi ca tatiyapadhāniyaṅgasamannāgamena uju assa. 
618441,125,715,60,73,1,111,13,Uju hontopi ca sakiṃ ujubhāvena santosaṃ anāpajjitvā yāvajīvaṃ punappunaṃ asithilakaraṇena suṭṭhutaraṃ uju assa. 
618442,125,715,74,80,1,36,5,"Asaṭhatāya vā uju, amāyāvitāya suhuju. "
618443,125,715,81,87,1,55,5,"Kāyavacīvaṅkappahānena vā uju, manovaṅkappahānena suhuju. "
618444,125,715,88,98,1,89,9,"Asantaguṇassa vā anāvikaraṇena uju, asantaguṇena uppannassa lābhassa anadhivāsanena suhuju. "
618445,125,715,99,109,1,103,10,Evaṃ ārammaṇalakkhaṇūpanijjhānehi purimadvayatatiyasikkhāhi payogāsayasuddhīhi ca uju ca suhuju ca assa. 
618446,125,716,2,15,1,56,11,"Na kevalañca uju ca suhuju ca, apica pana subbaco ca assa. "
618447,125,716,16,69,1,235,39,"Yo hi puggalo‘‘ idaṃ na kātabban’’ ti vutto‘‘ kiṃ te diṭṭhaṃ, kiṃ te sutaṃ, ko me hutvā vadasi, kiṃ upajjhāyo ācariyo sandiṭṭho sambhatto vā’’ ti vadati, tuṇhībhāvena vā taṃ viheṭheti, sampaṭicchitvā vā na tathā karoti, so visesādhigamassa dūre hoti. "
618448,125,716,70,114,1,248,33,"Yo pana ovadiyamāno‘‘ sādhu, bhante, suṭṭhu vuttaṃ, attano vajjaṃ nāma duddasaṃ hoti, punapi maṃ evarūpaṃ disvā vadeyyātha anukampaṃ upādāya, cirassaṃ me tumhākaṃ santikā ovādo laddho’’ ti vadati, yathānusiṭṭhañca paṭipajjati, so visesādhigamassa avidūre hoti. "
618449,125,716,115,124,1,65,9,Tasmā evaṃ parassa vacanaṃ sampaṭicchitvā karonto subbaco ca assa. 
618450,125,717,2,9,1,30,6,"Yathā ca suvaco, evaṃ mudu assa. "
618451,125,717,10,30,1,206,19,{Mudū}ti gahaṭṭhehi dūtagamanappahiṇagamanādīsu niyuñjiyamāno tattha mudubhāvaṃ akatvā thaddho hutvā vattapaṭipattiyaṃ sakalabrahmacariye ca mudu assa suparikammakatasuvaṇṇaṃ viya tattha tattha viniyogakkhamo. 
618452,125,717,31,44,1,101,11,Atha vā {mudū}ti abhākuṭiko uttānamukho sukhasambhāso paṭisanthāravutti sutitthaṃ viya sukhāvagāho assa. 
618453,125,717,45,64,1,153,16,"Na kevalañca mudu, apica pana anatimānī assa, jātigottādīhi atimānavatthūhi pare nātimaññeyya, sāriputtatthero viya caṇḍālakumārakasamena cetasā vihareyyāti. "
618454,125,718,2,32,1,204,23,144. Evaṃ bhagavā santaṃ padaṃ abhisamecca viharitukāmassa tadadhigamāya vā paṭipajjamānassa visesato āraññakassa bhikkhuno ekaccaṃ karaṇīyaṃ vatvā puna tatuttaripi vattukāmo‘‘ santussako cā’’ ti dutiyaṃ gāthamāha. 
618455,125,719,2,17,1,103,11,Tattha ‘‘ santuṭṭhī ca kataññutā’’ ti ettha vuttappabhedena dvādasavidhena santosena santussatīti santussako. 
618456,125,719,18,32,1,84,11,"Atha vā tussatīti tussako, sakena tussako, santena tussako, samena tussakoti santussako. "
