618601,125,747,2,28,1,145,16,151. Evaṃ mettābhāvanāya vaḍḍhanaṃ dassetvā idāni taṃ bhāvanamanuyuttassa viharato iriyāpathaniyamābhāvaṃ dassento āha‘‘ tiṭṭhaṃ caraṃ… pe… adhiṭṭheyyā’’ ti. 
618602,125,748,2,64,1,301,34,"Tassattho – evametaṃ mettaṃ mānasaṃ bhāvento so‘‘ nisīdati pallaṅkaṃ ābhujitvā, ujuṃ kāyaṃ paṇidhāyā’’ tiādīsu( dī. ni.2.374; ma. ni.1.107; vibha.508) viya iriyāpathaniyamaṃ akatvā yathāsukhaṃ aññataraññatarairiyāpathabādhanavinodanaṃ karonto tiṭṭhaṃ vā caraṃ vā nisinno vā sayāno vā yāvatā vigatamiddho assa, atha etaṃ mettājhānassatiṃ adhiṭṭheyya. "
618603,125,749,2,20,1,93,13,Atha vā evaṃ mettābhāvanāya vaḍḍhanaṃ dassetvā idāni vasībhāvaṃ dassento āha‘‘ tiṭṭhaṃ caran’’ ti. 
618604,125,749,21,37,1,116,16,Vasippatto hi tiṭṭhaṃ vā caraṃ vā nisinno vā sayāno vā yāvatā iriyāpathena etaṃ mettājhānassatiṃ adhiṭṭhātukāmo hoti. 
618605,125,749,38,68,1,201,27,"Atha vā tiṭṭhaṃ vā caraṃ vāti na tassa ṭhānādīni antarāyakarāni honti, apica kho so yāvatā etaṃ mettājhānassatiṃ adhiṭṭhātukāmo hoti, tāvatā vitamiddho hutvā adhiṭṭhāti, natthi tassa tattha dandhāyitattaṃ. "
618606,125,749,69,80,1,59,8,"Tenāha‘‘ tiṭṭhaṃ caraṃ nisinno va sayāno, yāvatāssa vitamiddho. "
