618610,125,752,2,40,1,264,27,"Tassattho – yvāyaṃ‘‘ sukhinova khemino hontū’’ tiādiṃ katvā yāva‘‘ etaṃ satiṃ adhiṭṭheyyā’’ ti saṃvaṇṇito mettāvihāro, etaṃ catūsu dibbabrahmaariyairiyāpathavihāresu niddosattā attanopi paresampi atthakarattā ca idha ariyassa dhammavinaye brahmavihāramāhu, seṭṭhavihāramāhūti. "
