619566,125,953,97,132,1,253,28,"Na kevalañca tassa santhavāto bhayaṃ jātaṃ, apica kho pana yadetaṃ kilesānaṃ nivāsaṭṭhena sāsavārammaṇaṃ‘‘ niketan’’ ti vuccati, idānissa bhinnasaṃvarattā atikkantamariyādattā suṭṭhutaraṃ tato niketā jāyate rajo, yena saṃkiliṭṭhacitto anayabyasanaṃ pāpuṇissati. "
